WEBVTT

00:00.201 --> 00:02.000
<i>Previously on</i>
<i>The Borgias...</i>

00:02.051 --> 00:05.192
<i>The French king had been struck</i>
<i>with the Neapolitan disease.</i>

00:05.292 --> 00:06.626
As we had hoped.

00:06.694 --> 00:09.195
King Charles cannot
remain in Naples forever.

00:09.229 --> 00:11.064
The House of Borgia is doomed.

00:11.098 --> 00:14.400
The arms of the House of Sforza
will remain where they belong.

00:14.435 --> 00:18.204
We shall subdue the
arrogance of the Sforzas.

00:18.238 --> 00:21.607
Force them back to
the arms of Rome.

00:21.642 --> 00:24.310
Lucrezia.

00:24.411 --> 00:27.013
My God! A peasant
to a pope's daughter?

00:28.215 --> 00:30.516
Let him be!
Let him be!

00:30.617 --> 00:33.152
He has a terror of food,
since the event.

00:33.220 --> 00:35.421
See him safe to the
monastery in Perugia.

00:35.456 --> 00:37.623
The brothers will arrange
his passage to Rome.

00:37.658 --> 00:39.125
This child has a father.

00:39.226 --> 00:40.326
A stable hand.

00:40.427 --> 00:41.728
Who has come to Rome.

00:41.829 --> 00:42.829
You loved him?

00:42.863 --> 00:44.230
I still do.

00:44.331 --> 00:46.032
You normally work at night?

00:46.066 --> 00:48.434
I must practise my art in
secret, Your Holiness.

00:48.469 --> 00:51.904
You are more Eve than Adam.

00:51.939 --> 00:55.241
We may have a
commission for you.

00:55.275 --> 00:56.843
These celebrations.

00:56.877 --> 00:58.845
Does anyone have any
idea of the cost?

00:58.946 --> 01:01.447
Can one put a price on joy?

01:01.548 --> 01:03.449
No, Holy Father.
It is priceless.

01:03.550 --> 01:07.120
Let Rome be full of joy!

01:07.154 --> 01:08.888
I would gladly
die for you both.

01:08.956 --> 01:11.858
So go now, my love.
I would have you live.

01:11.892 --> 01:15.261
And Lucrezia?
Would you marry her again?

01:15.362 --> 01:17.096
In time.

01:17.164 --> 01:20.066
I mean you no harm, kind sir,
whoever you may be.

01:20.100 --> 01:21.300
Suicide.

01:21.368 --> 01:23.469
A sin even the
pope can't forgive.

01:23.504 --> 01:25.671
Dead men can't confess.

01:27.374 --> 01:32.989
[♪]

